<HEADLINE> London Stocks Close at Record High / British Stocks  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LONDON (AP) -- Share prices closed Monday at a record high on the  
London Stock Exchange. 
</P>
<P>
	The Financial Times-Stock Exchange 100-share index was up 94.7  
points, or 1.5 percent, at 6,515.3, buoyed by bullish expectations 
in New York. 
</P>
<P>
	Provisional volume was 1.3 billion shares, compared with 1.48  
billion shares Friday. 
</P>
</TEXT>
