longer traded separately, though they remain in use. Based on euro 
rates, the dollar is worth: 1.8392 German marks, up from 1.8322; 
6.1685 French francs, up from 6.1448; 2.0723 Dutch guilders, up 
from 2.0644; and 1,820.83 Italian lire, up from 1,813.84. 
</P>
